ke/|archive-date=19 November 2016|url-status=live}}\n* For \"Peligro\": {{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/artist/52374/giggs-ft-dave/|title=GIGGS FT. DAVE {{!}} full Official Chart History|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=22 January 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122145022/https://www.officialcharts.com/artist/52374/giggs-ft-dave/|archive-date=22 January 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[UK R&B Chart|UK<br />R&B]]<br /><ref name=\"RandB\">Peak R&B chart positions in the UK:\n* For \"Samantha\": {{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/r-and-b-singles-chart/20170203/114/|title=Official R&B Singles Chart Top 40: 03 February 2017 - 09 February 2017|date=3 February 2017|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=20 August 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190820225349/https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/r-and-b-singles-chart/20170203/114/|archive-date=20 August 2019|url-status=live}}\n* For \"18HUNNA\": {{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/r-and-b-singles-chart/20190111/114/|title=Official R&B Singles Chart Top 40: 11 January 2019 - 17 January 2019|date=11 January 2019|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=12 January 2019}}\n* For \"Thiago Silva\": {{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/r-and-b-singles-chart/20190712/114/|title=Official R&B Singles Chart Top 40 - 12 July 2019 - 18 July 2019|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=19 July 2019}}\n* For \"Nothing On You\": {{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/r-and-b-singles-chart/20190802/114/|title=Official R&B Singles Chart Top 40 - 02 August 2019 - 08 August 2019|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=3 August 2019}}\n* For \"Professor X\": {{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/r-and-b-singles-chart/20190920/114/|title=Official R&B Singles Chart Top 40 - 20 September 2019 - 26 September 2019|publisher